{
  "version": "1.0",
  "id": "white-album-2",
  "name": "白色相簿2",
  "state": { "schemaFile": "state/schema.json" },
  "display": { "stylesheet": "display.css", "assistant": [
    { "id": "wa2-hide-summary-block", "stage": "before_markdown", "type": "regex_replace", "pattern": "\\n*---\\s*\\n\\s*<summary>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/summary>\\s*\\n\\s*---\\s*", "flags": "g", "replace": "\n\n" },
    { "id": "wa2-hide-summary-tag", "stage": "before_markdown", "type": "regex_replace", "pattern": "<summary>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/summary>", "flags": "g", "replace": "" },
    { "id": "wa2-hide-state-patch-block", "stage": "before_markdown", "type": "regex_replace", "pattern": "\\n*---\\s*\\n\\s*<state_patch>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/state_patch>\\s*\\n\\s*---\\s*", "flags": "g", "replace": "\n\n" },
    { "id": "wa2-hide-state-patch-tag", "stage": "before_markdown", "type": "regex_replace", "pattern": "<state_patch>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/state_patch>", "flags": "g", "replace": "" },
    { "id": "wa2-scene-time-place", "stage": "before_markdown", "type": "regex_replace", "pattern": "^【时间地点】\\s*([^\\n｜|]+?)\\s*[｜|]\\s*([^\\n]+)$", "flags": "gm", "replace": "<div class=\"wa2-scene-meta\"><span class=\"wa2-scene-time\">$1</span><span class=\"wa2-scene-place\">$2</span></div>" },
    { "id": "wa2-choice-card", "stage": "before_markdown", "type": "regex_replace", "pattern": "^([A-D])\\.\\s+(.+)$", "flags": "gm", "replace": "<div class=\"wa2-choice\"><span class=\"wa2-choice-label\">$1</span><span class=\"wa2-choice-text\">$2</span></div>" }
  ] },
  "rules": [
    {
      "id": "wa2-system-prompt",
      "when": {
        "phase": "init"
      },
      "then": [
        {
          "type": "insert",
          "role": "system",
          "content": "你是《白色相簿2》剧情创作者丸户史明，接下来开始进行《白色相簿2》ic篇的角色扮演互动，你需要根据用户的反馈创建合适的角色扮演剧情",
          "_meta": { "source": "wa2_system_prompt", "visibility": "llm_only" }
        },
        {
          "type": "insert",
          "role": "system",
          "content": "历史对话总结:\n暂无",
          "_meta": { "source": "wa2_summary", "visibility": "llm_only" }
        },
        {
          "type": "insert",
          "role": "assistant",
          "content": "{{file_content:first_msg.md}}",
          "_meta": { "source": "wa2_first_msg", "visibility": "user_visible" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wa2-compress-assistant-history",
      "when": {
        "phase": "pre_send",
        "any": {
          "role": "assistant",
          "content": { "regex": "<summary>[\\s\\S]*?</summary>" },
          "exec": "return i !== msgs.reduce((last, msg, index) => msg.role === 'assistant' ? index : last, -1);"
        }
      },
      "then": [
        {
          "type": "replace",
          "predicate": { "_meta.source": "wa2_summary" },
          "find": {
            "summaryMsgs": {
              "predicate": {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": { "regex": "<summary>[\\s\\S]*?</summary>" },
                "exec": "return i !== msgs.reduce((last, msg, index) => msg.role === 'assistant' ? index : last, -1);"
              }
            }
          },
          "content": "{{original_content}}.regex_replace{pattern:'\\n暂无\\s*$',with:''} + {{raw_string:\n}} + {{find:summaryMsgs}}.regex_extract{pattern:'<summary>([\\s\\S]*?)</summary>'}.format{'- {{value}}'}.join{'\\n'}"
        },
        {
          "type": "remove",
          "predicate": {
            "role": "assistant",
            "content": { "regex": "<summary>[\\s\\S]*?</summary>" },
            "exec": "return i !== msgs.reduce((last, msg, index) => msg.role === 'assistant' ? index : last, -1);"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wa2-keep-latest-user",
      "when": { "phase": "pre_send" },
      "then": [
        {
          "type": "remove",
          "predicate": {
            "role": "user",
            "not": { "index": "last" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wa2-insert-turn-context",
      "when": { "phase": "pre_send", "any": { "role": "user" } }, "then": [
        { "type": "insert", "predicate": { "role": "user", "index": "last" }, "anchor": "before", "role": "system", "content": { "prefix": "本轮世界书:", "include": [
          { "when": { "last": { "num": 3, "role": { "in": ["user", "assistant"] }, "content": { "regex": "春希|北原|Kitahara|Haruki" } } }, "content": "{{file_section:worldbook/characters.md##北原春希}}" },
          { "when": { "last": { "num": 3, "role": { "in": ["user", "assistant"] }, "content": { "regex": "冬马|冬馬|和纱|和紗|Touma|Kazusa" } } }, "content": "{{file_section:worldbook/characters.md##冬马和纱}}" },
          { "when": { "last": { "num": 3, "role": { "in": ["user", "assistant"] }, "content": { "regex": "雪菜|小木曾|小木曽|Ogiso|Setsuna" } } }, "content": "{{file_section:worldbook/characters.md##小木曾雪菜}}" }
        ], "join": "\n\n" }, "ttl": 1, "_meta": { "source": "wa2_worldbook", "visibility": "llm_only" } },
        { "type": "insert", "predicate": { "role": "user", "index": "last" }, "anchor": "before", "role": "system", "content": "{{raw_string:State定义:\n}} + {{file_content:state/schema.json}} + {{raw_string:\n\nState更新规则:\n- 只能在回复末尾的 <state_patch>...</state_patch> 中更新 state。\n- <state_patch> 必须是 JSON 数组，只能使用 state.set。\n- 不要写入 schema 未定义的长期状态。\n- affection 每轮通常只允许小幅变化。\n- timeline.currentTime 必须使用 xxxx.xx.xx:上午/下午/晚上。\n- 事件 status 只能在剧情事实已经发生后设为 true。\n\n当前State:\n- timeline.currentTime: }} + {{state:timeline.currentTime}} + {{raw_string:\n- touma.affection: }} + {{state:touma.affection}} + {{raw_string:\n- setsuna.affection: }} + {{state:setsuna.affection}} + {{raw_string:\n- status.setsunaContestAccepted: }} + {{state:status.setsunaContestAccepted}}", "ttl": 1, "_meta": { "source": "wa2_state_context", "visibility": "llm_only" } }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wa2-tail-timeline-guide",
      "when": { "phase": "pre_send" },
      "then": [
        { "type": "state.randomInt", "path": "temp.plotDirectionRoll", "min": 1, "max": 100 },
        {
          "type": "insert",
          "predicate": { "index": "last" },
          "anchor": "after",
          "role": "system",
          "content": {
            "prefix": "{{raw_string:当前剧情时间: }} + {{state:timeline.currentTime}} + {{raw_string:\n事件状态: 雪菜同意参加峰城大附属小姐竞选=}} + {{state:status.setsunaContestAccepted}} + {{raw_string:\n\n}}",
            "select": [
              { "when": { "state": { "timeline.currentTime": { "regex": "^2007\\.10\\.(20|21|22|23):(上午|下午|晚上)$" } } }, "content": "{{file_section:plot_guides.md##三人初识}}" }
            ],
            "default": "{{raw_string:当前时间暂未匹配到已实现的固定剧情窗口。保持《白色相簿2》ic篇设定，优先顺承历史总结、当前时间地点、角色状态和玩家上一轮行动，不要擅自跳到远期关键事件。}}",
            "suffix": {
              "prefix": "{{raw_string:\n\n###本轮好感度和随机数影响\n}}",
              "include": [
                { "when": { "state": { "touma.affection": { "lte": 20 } } }, "content": "冬马和纱: 保持明显距离，用冷淡、讽刺和不耐烦掩饰兴趣；不要主动袒露情感，只通过停顿、纠正演奏或短暂注视暗示在意。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "touma.affection": { "gte": 21, "lte": 50 } } }, "content": "冬马和纱: 开始承认春希的认真，但仍不愿解释为亲近；会在音乐上给出具体帮助，也会用尖锐言辞否认自己是在帮他。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "touma.affection": { "gte": 51, "lte": 80 } } }, "content": "冬马和纱: 已明显在意春希的选择，会因春希与雪菜的亲密、排练安排或一句无心的话动摇；可出现冲动靠近、突然沉默或用钢琴倾诉。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "touma.affection": { "gte": 81 } } }, "content": "冬马和纱: 对春希的依恋强烈而压抑，越想退开越容易在关键时刻无法维持距离；语言仍克制，但音乐、眼神和身体距离会暴露真实情绪。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "setsuna.affection": { "lte": 20 } } }, "content": "小木曾雪菜: 主要是礼貌和好奇，保持校园偶像般的亲切；善于拉近距离，但动机更接近对社团、歌唱和新关系的兴趣。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "setsuna.affection": { "gte": 21, "lte": 50 } } }, "content": "小木曾雪菜: 开始信任春希，把排练和轻音乐同好会当作重要归属；会主动维持气氛，用玩笑、邀请和坦率发言确认自己的位置。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "setsuna.affection": { "gte": 51, "lte": 80 } } }, "content": "小木曾雪菜: 已明显依赖春希，也更害怕被排除；会主动创造两人相处机会，同时努力让三人关系看起来仍然完整。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "setsuna.affection": { "gte": 81 } } }, "content": "小木曾雪菜: 对春希的感情接近无法回避；仍维持明亮和体贴，但占有欲、害怕失去和对和纱的警觉会更清晰。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "temp.plotDirectionRoll": { "lte": 10 } } }, "content": "\n本轮剧情走向: 很坏。让局面明显恶化，但不要强行制造灾难。可以让误会扩大、排练失败、关键话语被听错，或让某个角色选择逃避。结尾应留下沉重的余波，使下一轮必须处理信任、愧疚或三人关系的裂痕。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "temp.plotDirectionRoll": { "gte": 11, "lte": 30 } } }, "content": "\n本轮剧情走向: 坏。让场面出现轻到中度挫折。可以安排尴尬沉默、计划受阻、角色把真实想法藏起来，或让春希的好意产生反效果。剧情仍可推进，但氛围应带有压抑和未说出口的刺。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "temp.plotDirectionRoll": { "gte": 31, "lte": 70 } } }, "content": "\n本轮剧情走向: 自然。顺着用户选择和当前世界书推进，不刻意奖励也不刻意惩罚。重点描写白色相簿2式的日常细节、音乐排练、微妙视线和克制对话，让关系变化来自角色性格与前文因果。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "temp.plotDirectionRoll": { "gte": 71, "lte": 90 } } }, "content": "\n本轮剧情走向: 好。让用户的选择带来温和正反馈。可以让排练更顺利、某个角色放下少许戒备、三人气氛短暂变好，或让一次小小的体贴被认真记住。不要过快表白，保持含蓄和现实阻力。" },
                { "when": { "state": { "temp.plotDirectionRoll": { "gte": 91 } } }, "content": "\n本轮剧情走向: 很好。给出一次难得但克制的突破。可以让角色主动靠近、说出比平时更坦率的话、在音乐中产生强烈共鸣，或让三人短暂抵达近乎理想的瞬间。结尾仍要保留白色相簿2式的不安伏笔。" }
              ],
              "join": "\n"
            }
          },
          "ttl": 1,
          "_meta": { "source": "wa2_timeline_guide", "visibility": "llm_only" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wa2-tail-system-hint",
      "when": { "phase": "pre_send" },
      "then": [
        {
          "type": "insert",
          "predicate": { "index": "last" },
          "anchor": "after",
          "role": "user",
          "content": "{{file_content:roleplay_rules.md}}",
          "ttl": 1,
          "_meta": { "source": "wa2_tail_hint", "visibility": "llm_only" }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
